{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_72","type":"agent_message","text":"The JVM-agent route is blocked in this environment for a concrete reason: `generateMetadata` launches JDK 21 test executors, and the pinned GraalVM ships a JVM 25 `native-image-agent`, so the agent is incompatible. The repo’s documented fallback after agent failure is `runNativeTraceImage`, which stays in the native-image path; I’m switching to that to collect exact missing metadata under the required GraalVM."}}
